---
title: Pan-Fried Steak Strips with Red Pepper Rice and Honey Lime Dressing
description: Zesty, sweet and sticky with a kick of Mexican spice, our pan-fried steak strips are packed with deliciousness. Think juicy, charred pepper, onion sizzled with garlic and tomato and rice bubbled with stock for an intensely rich flavour all whipped up and on plates in 25 minutes. Winner winner, steak for dinner.
